{"tid":1524662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】急救員藏有攻擊性武器被捕　檢獲三把剪刀和生理鹽水","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:27:51.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"11d093cb18a98e95920283cf5d2f19d5bc0a9e87","tid":1524662,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3227905/org/ec4c15cf48de3f26490b6765de4b400a.jpg/nvQgzegVMjJ_F9MOMeCOGbfYbjqlc2Rv-Zc0pvmXNKY?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3227905%2Forg%2Fec4c15cf48de3f26490b6765de4b400a.jpg%2FnvQgzegVMjJ_F9MOMeCOGbfYbjqlc2Rv-Zc0pvmXNKY%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=afd4a670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方進入觀塘站，有身穿黑衣的人被搜身，引起在場人士不滿。觀塘站入閘機旁一塊玻璃及站內閉路電視被破壞。月台懷疑有人被捕，惟警方將記者全部趕離地鐵站，有一段時間未能得知被捕人士情況。警方其後將他帶上警車，<span style=\"color: red;\">該名被捕男子姓簡，自稱急救員，表示警方從他背囊搜出三把剪刀及生理鹽水，警方以涉嫌「藏有攻擊性武器」及「非法集結」將他拘捕。</span>他指警方對他很禮貌。  港鐵公布，因應觀塘線和荃灣線沿線多區的突發情況，多個車站更受到不同程度的破壞，觀塘線和荃灣線列車服務現時暫停。港鐵解釋，因為站內發生乘客衝突，對其他乘客和員工的安全帶來威脅，車站啓動了疏散程序。"},{"pid":"dc4140e4662e80c3dca69bb1772dd92ec9fcd63a","tid":1524662,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a070edaf74b9c33f67547157d5c4ec9c2cb50cef","tid":1524662,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27be20568d297a396178e7821ba9b75935695827","tid":1524662,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母軍政府"},{"pid":"bcbe01cb9c9c634d041ac5f9ce807050d35fc5f7","tid":1524662,"uid":81334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"d魔警習慣用口咬開d繃帶？"},{"pid":"7a33b917b424cb0d8190dc858e652ec19607f432","tid":1524662,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/onccMainWebapp/videoShare.faces?pub=ontvhk&amp;pubType=video&amp;shareType=facebook&amp;createTime=1567258310&amp;videoId=ONS190831-14079-29-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2FonccMainWebapp%2FvideoShare.faces%3Fpub%3Dontvhk%26pubType%3Dvideo%26shareType%3Dfacebook%26createTime%3D1567258310%26videoId%3DONS190831-14079-29-M&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=aabde38a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/onccMainWebapp/videoShare.faces?pub=ontvhk&amp;pubType=video&amp;shareType=facebook&amp;createTime=1567258310&amp;videoId=ONS190831-14079-29-M</a>"},{"pid":"52d824c0de19bdbaf936aeb50cbb488ea5161900","tid":1524662,"uid":152222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"肯打狗未？"},{"pid":"6d72b7509ebd48484f24920ec130aa31c803cbf8","tid":1524662,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"屌係咪戇鳩架<img src=\"/asset